Instalacia a spustenie projektu (Docker / Laravel Sail)
==================================================

Tento projekt bezi cez Laravel Sail (Docker) a pouziva Vite na frontend assety.

Pozadavky
----------
- Docker, Ubuntu

3) Vytvorenie a uprava .env
---------------------------
V korenovom priecinku projektu:

cp .env.example .env

Uprav .env podla potreby (DB nazov, hesla, pripadne porty).

4) Spustenie kontajnerov (Sail)
-------------------------------
./vendor/bin/sail up -d

5) Instalacia backend zavislosti (Composer v kontejnery)
--------------------------------------------------------
./vendor/bin/sail composer install

6) Vygenerovanie APP_KEY
------------------------
./vendor/bin/sail artisan key:generate

7) Migracie databazy
--------------------
./vendor/bin/sail artisan migrate

8) Frontend build (Vite) â€“ nutne kvoli manifest.json
----------------------------------------------------
Ak sa po otvoreni stranky zobrazi chyba:
Vite manifest not found at: public/build/manifest.json

sprav build assetov:

./vendor/bin/sail npm install
./vendor/bin/sail npm run build

9) Otvorenie aplikacie
----------------------
Po spusteni Sailu je aplikacia dostupna typicky na:
http://localhost

Uzitoce prikazy
----------------
Zastavenie kontajnerov:
./vendor/bin/sail down

Vycistenie cache:
./vendor/bin/sail artisan config:clear
./vendor/bin/sail artisan cache:clear
./vendor/bin/sail artisan route:clear
./vendor/bin/sail artisan view:clear

Najcastejsie problemy
---------------------
- Chyba vendor/autoload.php:
  ./vendor/bin/sail composer install

- Vite manifest not found (public/build/manifest.json):
  ./vendor/bin/sail npm install
  ./vendor/bin/sail npm run build
